{"tid":1179192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來喺中國，可以缺席審判。。","createTime":"2019-05-31T02:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T09:06:29.000Z","uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dee41435a52e676d2be8dde5d6e6f055b9399db9","tid":1179192,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：香港人不必擔心中國引渡啦，中國原來可以缺席審判，不過判決目前無法在香港地區執行而已。<br />\n<br />\n大家也許無留意到，二〇一八年十月二十六日，中國人大通過《刑事訴訟法》修正草案，貪污行賄罪、妨礙國家安全罪、恐怖活動罪這三項罪名，可以執行缺席審訊。<br />\n<br />\n先前規定，境外逃逸人員必須回國或引渡歸案後才可展開司法程序的。注意，這三項罪名，正是逃犯引渡條例修訂要針對的居港人士的罪名。<br />\n<br />\n昨日，林鄭月娥說，引渡犯人可以考慮在香港坐監，就是配合中國法例在去年的修訂。如此觀之，引渡未必需要。<br />\n<br />\n大陸火速判案之後，在香港用《刑事事宜相互法律協助條例》（目前一併與《逃犯引渡條例》修訂中！）在香港執行，即刻在香港充公財產，在香港坐監，引渡回中國也不必了。<br />\n<br />\n中國得到抄家的錢，香港代出監獄錢。這是終極雙贏方案，陳雲預告給香港人知道。大家開開心心去聯署示威啦。"},{"pid":"04e07c087e09b1c6b5c139aa39731e1673357298","tid":1179192,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:53:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/107018?fbclid=IwAR3ZZgr7H0TOWyDrlBXcRF_emR_3uJTzjihxgnL5qIzri-l4GHTgGI-WWJk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F107018%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ZZgr7H0TOWyDrlBXcRF_emR_3uJTzjihxgnL5qIzri-l4GHTgGI-WWJk&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=35c0c186\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/107018?fbclid=IwAR3ZZgr7H0TOWyDrlBXcRF_emR_3uJTzjihxgnL5qIzri-l4GHTgGI-WWJk</a>"},{"pid":"86d84b446ef37e1924347c00c2048d5612125298","tid":1179192,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"到時離線炒家都好方便"},{"pid":"23f70ba2797a77cf9a361bfd5b0b5891a13a7154","tid":1179192,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:38:20.000Z","msg":"［陽光法治 超英趕美］上年支國發明咗&lsquo;缺席審判&rsquo; 貪污賄賂、嚴重危害國家安全、恐怖活動 冇原告照樣可以開審<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1178375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1178375</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"519d10e7a20dcd484d26c5d8ba2477c100a84532","tid":1179192,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"預早搵人搞你<br />\n可以審都唔洗審"},{"pid":"79993a2c005688137b1bf02c06cf64c60ae5ad0a","tid":1179192,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"共產黨殺到來"},{"pid":"d7ff6a283cc5e5b7399dedeceaf2a18fe0bff2e7","tid":1179192,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23f70ba2797a77cf9a361bfd5b0b5891a13a7154","tid":1179192,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:38:20.000Z","msg":"［陽光法治 超英趕美］上年支國發明咗&lsquo;缺席審判&rsquo; 貪污賄賂、嚴重危害國家安全、恐怖活動 冇原告照樣可以開審<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1178375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1178375</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}